How To Skip Payments On Your Mortgage, Auto Loan And Credit CardsThe federal government is ordering mortgage companies to allow people who have lost their job or income to make reduced payments or to skip payments.
You tell them you are having a financial hardship because of the coronavirus and you need to make reduced payments or skip payments and be put into what's called a forbearance plan.